data.value:
AgentHelper is a tiny utility to help the good people of Esri Canada Technical Support get the question "Am I logged in or not?" off their minds and focus on more important questions like "What code should I use to close this case?". This tool will show a small icon in the System Tray of a phone handset indicating the current status of the Cisco Agent Desktop application. You can also use this tool to change your status. For that, AutoHotKey must be installed. Get it at www.autohotkey.com
Developed by Amr Eldib. Copyrights are reserved in the hope that this will turn to a million dollars business.
